title: Built to Spill - Twin Falls Alt Lyrics
description:
Most fans of Built to Spill know the song Twin Falls, but most people don't know that when performed live Doug Martsch sometimes changes the last lines of the song from "It doesn't bother me" to "Except for in my dreams" making the song a bit more sorrowful.



Included in this torrent are two live performances where the lyrics are changed:


Built to Spill - Twin Falls - Don't Fear the Reaper.flac
Built to Spill - Twin Falls - Some (Mother's Day).mp3




Both are about as best that can be expected from live recordings.
